column2: Election Commission of Malaysia (SPR), Tindak Malaysia (2025), Dr Asyraf Wajdi Dusuki

The results are derived from the YB Dr Asyraf Wajdi Dusuki Facebook Post (https://web.facebook.com/drasyrafwajdidusuki/videos/2553822151627796). Limited validation was performed. The focus is only on the ordinary vote, not early vote and postal vote data. Total votes for BN is 11065,  PN is 6059 and PSM is 1106. Unofficial data has undercounted BN by 94 votes, overestimated PN by 100 votes and underestimated PSM by 45 votes. TindakMalaysia Network Services PLT is not responsible for errors and omissions
